snippet.title: Star Wars Mod: Galactic Warfare v1.0 Release Trailer
snippet.description:
blackMonkeys.de is happy to present our final version of Star Wars Mod: Galactic Warfare.

After all the modding, mapping, scripting, gaming, and drinking, it is done! We hope you will enjoy the mod which is a non-profit project operated by fans. Star Wars, its characters, locations, weapons and all associated items are the intellectual property of Lucasfilm. ©2009 Lucasfilm Ltd. & ™ All rights reserved.
